overview: This series introduces you to ladies for whom too much is never enough. Featured cover girl Gianna Dior loves the money she earns as an influencer and relishes thirsty attention from her male followers. But when a fan sends Gianna a DM she can't ignore, the obsession goes deep enough to make her the thirsty one. Jane Wilde, Shona River, and Alicia Williams are all grabbing a hold of as much muscle as they can get their hands on.
title: Ample
